description:
Friday November 21, 2008.

Today, Alex talks with Debbie McKee of End the Fed, Lindsey Williams the author of The Energy Non-Crisis who predicted oil prices would drop, American Farm Bureau Federation director of Regulatory Relations Rick Krause, and Alex Jones Show regular Bob Chapman.

Hour-1: News & Open Lines
Hour-2: Debbie McKee then Lindsey Williams
Hour-3: Rick Krause
Hour-4: Bob Chapman
